chunkloader (0.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * webpack / Next.js chunk extraction (standard chunks, webpack runtime,
    __BUILD_MANIFEST as function or object, "modern" chunks).
  * Native ESM support (Framer / rolldown / rollup / Vite): recursive crawl
    of the module import graph, including backtick dynamic imports.
  * Flutter Web support: download every resource listed in
    flutter_service_worker.js (main.dart.js, assets, fonts, canvaskit, ...).
  * Automatic entry detection from a page URL, parallel downloads.

 -- Sn0wAlice <github@sn0w.io>  Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
